snippet.title: SimFarm - gameplay
snippet.description:
SimFarm was made by maxis in 1993:
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sim_farm

You can download it legally here:
http://www.abandonia.com/en/games/45/SimFarm.html
but it would be a good idea to download dosbox also to run the game in.

 I wanted to make a whole play-though of this game. But then i realized that i would and could never finish this game. So i think i´ll just keep it at one video.
